{"tid":107460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以幫到我","createTime":"2017-02-04T13:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T14:08:15.000Z","uid":62590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76c2f2ba538aa29b840837dec3d54a3fb1e6d51a","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"我住係西洋菜南街附近<br />\n最近半年行人專用區<br />\n大嬸大叔個喇叭聲越黎越大聲<br />\n試過同佢地理論俾人屌返轉頭<br />\n報過警唔受理<br />\n我精神受壓力 長期嘈音真係我屋企講野都就黎聽唔到<br />\n仲要佢地d歌聲又尖又走音<br />\n有咩方法可以救到我<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係係屋企連續5個鐘聽佢地聽到想死"},{"pid":"c838c5521a14273e771db36e652a3c5c3ae61bbd","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"其實成日d人行街經過同朋友講野都聽唔到<br />\n好多人行過要掩耳<br />\n點解仲有咁多人捐錢俾佢地<br />\n助紂為虐"},{"pid":"8311076951e4614edb42747eeb57f2976ffe2862","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b70e0528420e15586fd1aadad074cfb69e7aaf","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0af39cf50014d98766ca45a809a0887c052fc7","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d239ed368962404ea2299bf719ea3de85674a963","tid":107460,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6945c5f32eb96cef5e9c8362dcae0680322ccd5b","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a62a98385404c2be4105c35caf58b1fec3e1ef1","tid":107460,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"落去同佢地隻揪"},{"pid":"6f55ecab03bbd0c9e204f4b7160429169098e2b7","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>必須處死嗰班賤畜。</blockquote><br />\n真係好辛苦<br />\n佢哋真係越黎越大聲<br />\n同一個位可以有三檔鬥大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef8f4b6f0a5aec014c87e6a80c4ccbf313e7b4e","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落去同佢地隻揪</blockquote><br />\n同佢哋講完<br />\n俾啲觀眾鬧返轉頭<br />\n話住附近就要忍<br />\n仲有人話做咩咁細聲"},{"pid":"db589abfebbdac3203fbe3f4307887f3300a716d","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"只要有人行過附近就知問題好嚴重<br />\n仲要長期星期六日<br />\n準時開唱5-6小時"},{"pid":"455ffc06f8a2aac51ccc3860de50db7e19cf16b4","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2b73dc7d464f5d9c400db9a4a94a027485a27a","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e141d36e44314893f3493b95d7f5afde708787da","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7885701ebe07b33cabbeee84e448eb6de4811153","tid":107460,"uid":62590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057412a172452b678eedf1ff4942638d30